    <text>
        <body>
            <p rend="align(center)"><persName>WOLF, HART &amp; CO.</persName>,</p>
            <p rend="align(center)"><placeName>LAW AND COLLECTION OFFICE</placeName>,</p>
            <p rend="align(center)"><placeName>Rooms 5 and 6, Washington Building</placeName>.</p>
            <p rend="align(center)"><placeName>CORNER OF SEVENTH STREET AND PENN.
                AVENUE</placeName>,</p>
            <p rend="align(right)"><placeName>Washington, D.C.</placeName>, <date>November 9th
                    1866</date></p>
            <p><placeName>Lock Box 51</placeName>.</p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">
                <addressee>Rev. Dr. Isaac Leeser</addressee>
            </p>
            <p rend="indent(2)">My Dear Sir</p>
            <p rend="indent(3)">I was sorry while in <placeName>Phila</placeName> not<lb/> to have
                had the pleasure of seeing you. I learned through<lb/> our mutual friends the
                    <persName>Miss Myers</persName> that your<lb/> health was not of the best, and
                that you absolutely<lb/> needed rest and relaxation and Consequently did not<lb/>
                intrude, therefore hope that your fears will prove<lb/> groundless, that you will
                have many years<lb/> of prosperity and increased usefulness before you.<lb/> Do not
                for a moment think that your labors<lb/> have been in vain, or that your
                disinterestedness has<lb/> not been appreciated. But be assured that there<lb/> are
                thousands of good &amp; true Israelites who<lb/> Cherish &amp; Esteem you. I am dear
                sir</p>
            <p rend="indent(2)">Truly yours</p>
            <p rend="indent(3)">
                <persName role="author">S. Wolf</persName>
            </p>
            <pb n="Envelope"/>
            <p>
                <placeName>Law and Collection Office</placeName>
            </p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">OF</p>
            <p>
                <persName>NEELY &amp; COLLIER</persName>
            </p>
            <p><placeName>Room No. 4 Washington <add>?</add></placeName>,</p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">
                <placeName>WASHINGTON, D.C.</placeName>
            </p>
            <p rend="indent(2)">
                <addressee>Rev Isaac Leeser</addressee>
            </p>
            <p rend="indent(2)">
                <placeName>1227 Walnut St</placeName>
            </p>
